    <title>Thousands of Samsung workers launch indefinite strike over pay </title>
    <content type="html">  

    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img alt="TOPSHOT-SKOREA-SAMSUNG-STRIKE" src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/LPAm8fMQW7F168kwZwheXVZBdGE=/100x0:7087x4658/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73452568/2160498481.0.jpg" /&gt;
